      <h1>Why Multiuploader</h1>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Efficiency:</strong> Designed to reduce time spent on bulk uploads and status checking.</li>
        <li><strong>User-Friendly:</strong> Simple workflows even with advanced automation behind the scenes.</li>
        <li><strong>Scalable:</strong> Handles growing volumes of files and targets without changing the process.</li>
        <li><strong>Extensible:</strong> Architecture supports adding new platforms and custom upload steps.</li>
        <li><strong>Modern Tech Stack:</strong> Combines Django, Three.js, and Chrome extension tooling for flexibility.</li>
      </ul>
